Package: sitools
Type: Package
Title: Format a number to a string with SI prefix
Version: 1.0
Date: 2012-01-09
Author: Jonas Stein, Ben Tupper
Maintainer: Jonas Stein <news@jonasstein.de>
Description: Format a number (or a list of numbers) 
to a string (or a list of strings) with SI prefix.

sistring(0.003, 5e9) 
[1] "3 m", "5 G"


